@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@aircraftCreatedId = {{createAircraft.response.body.id}}


### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/aircraft/decolamos

###

### GET all aircraft
GET {{baseUrl}}/aircraft

###

